    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak, featuring the S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains tight, with recent inspections confirming rear subframe integrity and refreshed suspension bushings. Performance is optimized by a linear power delivery and an 8,000 RPM redline, offering a visceral driving experience for those who prioritize tactile feedback and engineering pedigree.",
